  "title": "Full Time Sales Associate",
  "description": "<p>Duchess Singapore is a luxury boutique specialising in curated vintage timepieces. We are looking for a passionate and customer-focused Full-Time Sales Associate to join our growing team.</p><p>Key Responsibilities:<br />• Provide excellent customer service and personalised watch consultations<br />• Handle walk-in customers, WhatsApp, and social media enquiries<br />• Assist in sales transactions and after-sales follow-ups<br />• Maintain cleanliness, visual merchandising, and product displays<br />• Support daily store operations and stock handling<br />• Create basic sales content (IG stories, simple product shots)</p><p>Requirements:<br />• Well-groomed, confident, and sales-oriented<br />• Retail or luxury sales experience preferred (training provided)<br />• Interest in watches, fashion, or luxury goods is a strong advantage<br />• Good communication skills <br />• Responsible, proactive, and a team player<br />• Able to commit on Sundays (Half Day) and peak retail hours<br />• Attractive <strong>4.5 day work week </strong></p><p>What We Offer:<br />• Basic salary + commission + incentives<br />• Staff purchase privileges<br />• Hands-on training in luxury vintage watches<br />• Friendly and supportive work environment<br /></p><p>Location: CBD Singapore (Marina One- The Heart, East Tower)</p><p>Employment Type: Full-Time</p>",
